fields.Title: WHIRLING F2 / DREAM 3
fields.Description: Ancient Reptilian Brain won't let you forget how low you've fallen.

fields.Title: START
input
You: "Why?"
fields.Dialogue Text: Why?

fields.Title: Pain Threshold: "And there's a lot of it. Ever prese..."
fields.Dialogue Text: And there's a lot of it. Ever present in your organs. It's like every one of them has their own *nasty* song to sing.

fields.Title: You: "I'm sorry, cells! It's all me! It's..."
fields.Dialogue Text: I'm sorry, cells! It's all me! It's my fault!

fields.Title: Ancient Reptilian Brain: "Sure, you do. They're all so friend..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Sure, you do. They're all so friendly, aren't they?

fields.Title: Ancient Reptilian Brain: "Oh yeah, baby. Frame your suffering..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Oh yeah, baby. Frame your suffering as a masterpiece. Only one problem -- no one's watching. It's boring, buddy, boring as death.

fields.Title: Volition: "Come now. Humans have earned your t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Come now. Humans have earned your trust. And you theirs...

fields.Title: Volition: "Some of them are. Some of them are..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Some of them are. Some of them are nice. Others are scared.

fields.Title: Drama: "Thou art honourable and just, sire...."
fields.Dialogue Text: Thou art honourable and just, sire. 'Tis the snakes who are vile! Hissing in the grass...

fields.Title: Empathy: "Maybe if you weren't so hard on you..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Maybe if you weren't so hard on yourself...

fields.Title: Limbic System: "*Now* you're finally thinking about..."
fields.Dialogue Text: *Now* you're finally thinking about something other than yourself. Let's see how far that'll get you.

fields.Title: Ancient Reptilian Brain: "There's no dignity here... only ref..."
fields.Dialogue Text: There's no dignity here... only reflections of your body mass. Flashes of the day. You keep coming back to yourself in the mirror -- but why? To admire all your *accomplishments*?

fields.Title: You: "I thought I was on the express to T..."
fields.Dialogue Text: I thought I was on the express to The Silence!

fields.Title: Ancient Reptilian Brain: "Now, you've gone off the rails, bab..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Now, you've gone off the rails, baby, now you're stuck sitting here by the tracks, admiring the wreck around you. You just can't help it: looking at yourself, the sum total of your *accomplishments*...

fields.Title: Ancient Reptilian Brain: "You're just stuck here. In the half..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You're just stuck here. In the half-world. Could try looking at other people. *Really* looking. But why would you want to start doing that?

fields.Title: You: "I will! I'm looking at people all t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: I will! I'm looking at people all the time. I like them.

fields.Title: Electrochemistry: "Maybe if you... you know... like......"
fields.Dialogue Text: Maybe if you... you know... like... TOOK A LOT OF DRUGS? Before you go to sleep. That'd do the trick...

fields.Title: You: "I'm an artist and liver damage is m..."
fields.Dialogue Text: I'm an artist and liver damage is my art.

fields.Title: Untitled hub
Ancient Reptilian Brain: "How many promises have *you* kept l..."
fields.Dialogue Text: How many promises have *you* kept lately, Sir Harry? To the great, see-through world, the tenderness?

fields.Title: Perception (Sight): "People are beautiful. Statuesque. P..."
fields.Dialogue Text: People are beautiful. Statuesque. Parodies and tragedies of themselves. A great democracy of creatures...

fields.Title: Empathy: "Every cell in your body is moaning..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Every cell in your body is moaning in agony, asking,  "What did we ever do to you?"

fields.Title: Variable["whirling.dream_3_empathy_cells"]
Variable["whirling.dream_3_empathy_cells"]
!(Variable["whirling.dream_3_empathy_cells"])
Ancient Reptilian Brain: "Oh yes. *They'll* check you out, gi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Oh yes. *They'll* check you out, give you some pills, make it all okay. The wonder-makers.

fields.Title: Ancient Reptilian Brain: "Let it! Let it!"
fields.Dialogue Text: Let it! Let it!

fields.Title: Limbic System: "It's your disgusting *body*. Even t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It's your disgusting *body*. Even through your sleep, you feel a vague discomfort suffusing it. Your belly and your sides are unpleasantly tender. You wish you could curl up into a foetal ball of safety, but you cannot -- because of the PAIN.

fields.Title: You: "These are my just desserts. I will..."
fields.Dialogue Text: These are my just desserts. I will endure this pain with *dignity*.

fields.Title: Drama: "Put on your prettiest face for the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Put on your prettiest face for the masses!

fields.Title: You: "It's all the system's fault. The sy..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It's all the system's fault. The system failed me.

fields.Title: You: "Human beings will *always* betray y..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Human beings will *always* betray you.

fields.Title: You: "This body's worthless anyway... no..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This body's worthless anyway... no one does anything nice to it.

fields.Title: You: "[Open your eyes.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: [Open your eyes.]

fields.Title: Limbic System: "And why might *that* be the case? W..."
fields.Dialogue Text: And why might *that* be the case? What love alights on such a bloated corpse-to-be?

fields.Title: Limbic System: "Oh, baby boy. You're already *in* t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Oh, baby boy. You're already *in* the other place. There's no nourishment for you tonight. Maybe tomorrow?

fields.Title: Rhetoric: "At least they're *interesting*. Eac..."
fields.Dialogue Text: At least they're *interesting*. Each one has a process just like yours, running in the space between their ears, full of secrets.

fields.Title: Untitled hub
Limbic System: "Yes, your body is a system, and and..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Yes, your body is a system, and and it's failing you because you're failing it.

fields.Title: You: "Wait, wasn't this the express to Fu..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Wait, wasn't this the express to Fuck-All-Borough?

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: Variable["whirling.dreamone_borough"]  and  Variable["whirling.dreamone_zero_holm"] == false  and  Variable["whirling.dreamone_the_silence"] == false

fields.Title: You: "Hey, what is this? I was on the exp..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Hey, what is this? I was on the express to Zero-Holm!

fields.Title: Limbic System: "You're not *cooperating* brother-ma..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You're not *cooperating* brother-man.

fields.Title: Limbic System: "Don't be stupid Harry, it's not hap..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Don't be stupid Harry, it's not happening. They don't make new *kidneys* and *livers* in hospital. All you've got to do is pray to god it passes -- while you *stare* at the flickering darkness.

fields.Title: You: "Just get me out of here then. Back..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Just get me out of here then. Back to the other place.

fields.Title: Limbic System: "...But it never seems to let *you*..."
fields.Dialogue Text: ...But it never seems to let *you* go, does it? Time to rise and wipe that shining sweat off as best you can. Gather your bearings. Rock and roll.

fields.Title: Limbic System: "Here we are again, my broken bird...."
fields.Dialogue Text: Here we are again, my broken bird. The waves are coming... carrying you away... but you can't go. No -- you have to stay. Always half-aware of yourself.

fields.Title: Logic: "That pain in your right side is you..."
fields.Dialogue Text: That pain in your right side is your enlarged liver, by the way. As for your kidneys... you've really been compounding the damage lately.

fields.Title: You: "No, please... Where is that blessed..."
fields.Dialogue Text: No, please... Where is that blessed nothingness? That sweet oblivion?

fields.Title: You: "I think I... need medical attention..."
fields.Dialogue Text: I think I... need medical attention.

fields.Title: Variable["doomed.radiocomputer_counted_headless"] == true
Variable["doomed.radiocomputer_counted_headless"] == true
!(Variable["doomed.radiocomputer_counted_headless"] == true)
Logic: "That pain in your right side is you..."
fields.Dialogue Text: That pain in your right side is your enlarged liver, by the way. As for your kidneys... you've really been compounding the damage lately. And, trust me, you don't want me to do the maths.

fields.Title: Conceptualization: "But this suffering -- it must have..."
fields.Dialogue Text: But this suffering -- it must have *some* kind of meaning... A story that will come out of it. Perhaps even a story that you will write yourself?

fields.Title: Logic: "Maybe if you cracked the damn thing..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Maybe if you cracked the damn thing, then you'd feel satisfied and tired. Holding the picture puzzle in your hands... complete!

fields.Title: Endurance: "Women. It's the women. Look out for..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Women. It's the women. Look out for the women. They're *oathbreakers*...

fields.Title: Ancient Reptilian Brain: "You had your chance, Harry-boy, and..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You had your chance, Harry-boy, and you missed it. Started thrashing around, acting all brave -- now the Dark Centre has vanished. You'll never get back to it.

fields.Title: Limbic System: "What do you think you're doing righ..."
fields.Dialogue Text: What do you think you're doing right now? Coming to some greater awareness? Look at all these lights! Blinking in and out of existence -- *thoughts*! You're just *pretending* that you're asleep, even to yourself. While the world goes on without you...
